=== Better_Approach ===
Instead of blanket bans, we could: # diagram: better_approach.png

Empower parents with tools and education—not surveillance.

Require platforms to offer meaningful controls—not just age gates.

Invest in physical social infrastructure—not just cut spending.

Teach digital literacy from childhood—not just block and hope.

Support families with ongoing resources—not one-time laws.

This approach:
• Respects family autonomy and values  
• Protects privacy for everyone
• Adapts to individual needs
• Builds long-term skills
• Doesn't create surveillance infrastructure

